<jobcard>
  <header issuedate="" version="15" logo="CCA-logo.bmp">
    <note>
      <cn>
        <para>
          <text style="1">注释：</text>
          <text>标有“*”的条目必须是国航授权的放行人员签署。</text>
        </para>
      </cn>
      <en>
        <para>
          <text style="1">NOTE:</text>
          <text>“*”This task must be signed off by Air China authorized dispatch personal.</text>
        </para>
      </en>
    </note>
    <caution>
      <cn>
        <para>
          <text style="1">注意：当进行以下维修工作时,必须严格遵守维护手册及相关维修文件的安全注意事项。</text>
        </para>
      </cn>
      <en>
        <para>
          <text style="1">Caution: When you do the maintenance work, you must obey the safety caution of the AMM and maintenance documents.</text>
        </para>
      </en>
    </caution>
  </header>
  <body>
    <model path="000043" no="1" titlecn="一般工作" titleen="General work">
      <pos path="000043000001" no="1" titlecn="一般工作" titleen="General work">
        <item path="000043000001000001" no="1">
          <cn>
            <para>
              <text>检查停机位周围无障碍物，附近地面无垃圾、石子等有可能吸入发动机的杂物。</text>
            </para>
          </cn>
          <en>
            <para>
              <text>Make sure that there are no unwanted materials (such as rubbish, block) around the engine air
inlet.</text>
            </para>
          </en>
        </item>
        <item path="000043000001000002" no="2">
          <cn>
            <para>
              <text>飞机停稳后挡好轮挡，通知机组松刹车。</text>
            </para>
          </cn>
          <en>
            <para>
              <text>Chock on after aircraft positioned, inform crew to release the parking brake.</text>
            </para>
          </en>
        </item>
        <item path="000043000001000003" no="3">
          <cn>
            <para>
              <text>放干饮用水。如果当日最低温度低于0℃时要立即放水并吹净饮用水系统，之后请关闭厨房
水笼头。</text>
            </para>
          </cn>
          <en>
            <para>
              <text>Drain the potable water. To drain water immediately and blow outif the lowest temperature of the
day is below 0℃, and make sure the kitchen water tap closed.</text>
            </para>
          </en>
        </item>
        <item path="000043000001000004" no="4">
          <cn>
            <para>
              <text>按机上文件清单检查并配齐所有文件。
</text>
              <text style="1">注:</text>
              <text>可以采用检查资料箱/袋的封条是否完好来替代该工作,如果封条完好,则无需开箱检查。</text>
            </para>
          </cn>
          <en>
            <para>
              <text>Check and ensure the documents listed in the table onboard for completeness.
</text>
              <text style="1">Note:</text>
              <text> Checking the status ofthe documents storage/bag seal can be used as the alternate for this
work. If the seal is not damaged, it is not necessary to open the seal to do the inspection.</text>
            </para>
          </en>
        </item>
      </pos>
    </model>
    <model path="000044" no="2" titlecn="飞机停放" titleen="Aircraft Parking">
      <pos path="000044000001" no="2" titlecn="飞机停放" titleen="Aircraft Parking">
        <item path="000044000001000001" no="1">
          <cn>
            <para>
              <text>按下列不同机型的要求为舱门加封条。
</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})" linestartsignid="1">(1)</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})">在登机梯（如装有）门、电子舱门、货舱门加封条（A320S）。
</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})" linestartsignid="2">(2)</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})">在电子舱门加封条（A330、A350）。
</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})" linestartsignid="3">(3)</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})">在登机梯(如装有)门、货舱门、电子舱门、前舱门加封条 (B737-600/700/800/MAX)。
</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})" linestartsignid="4">(4)</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})">在主电子舱门加封条（B747、B777、B787）。</text>
            </para>
          </cn>
          <en>
            <para>
              <text>Seal the doors for the individual A/C types.
</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})" linestartsignid="1">(1)</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})">Seal at airstairs door (if installed), E/Ebays doors, cargo doors (A320S).
</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})" linestartsignid="2">(2)</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})">Seal at E/E bays doors (A330, A350).
</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})" linestartsignid="3">(3)</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})">Seal at airstairs door (if installed), cargo doors, E/E bays door, nose compartment door</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})" linestartsignid="3">(3)</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})">(B737-600/700/800/MAX).
</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})" linestartsignid="4">(4)</text>
              <text islinestarttype="2" linestartsign="&amp;({num})">Seal at main E/E bays doors (B747, B777, B787).</text>
            </para>
          </en>
        </item>
        <item path="000044000001000002" no="2">
          <cn>
            <para>
              <text>绕机一周检查，确信地面设备已撤离。</text>
            </para>
          </cn>
          <en>
            <para>
              <text>Walk around the aircraft, check all the ground equipment removed.</text>
            </para>
          </en>
        </item>
        <item path="000044000001000003" no="3">
          <cn>
            <para>
              <text>将飞机交给护卫。</text>
            </para>
          </cn>
          <en>
            <para>
              <text>Transfer the aircraft to the guarder.</text>
            </para>
          </en>
        </item>
      </pos>
    </model>
  </body>
</jobcard>